the compiler for a language whose source is human text, written as a module named human_compiler that a separate repl imports whole, so it exposes:

- ROOT (the directory the module sits in),
- LANG
- PROGS
- CACHE and BUILD beneath it
- MODEL_ID,
- the exception Malformed,
- the class Node,

and the functions: 
- lang_text, 
- cached, 
- call, 
- call_json, 
- serialize, 
- generate, 
- tally, 
- caused_by, 
- project, 
- propose, 
- lower, 
- build and raises, 

and nothing else;